	(43,1,'2013-10-01 23:57:27','2013-10-01 23:57:27','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAG Design Group LAUNCHES a new website forAlameda Contra Costa Trial Lawyers Association .\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Web Design Walnut Creek for ACCTLA\" href=\"www.ACCTLA.org\" target=\"_blank\">www.ACCTLA.org</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://agdesigngroup.ag/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/ACCTLA.jpg\"><a href=\"http://agdesigngroup.ag/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/ACCTLA_before_after.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-383\" alt=\"ACCTLA_before_after\" src=\"http://agdesigngroup.ag/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/ACCTLA_before_after-300x228.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"228\" /></a></a>\r\n\r\nThe Alameda Contra Costa Trial Lawyers Association is widely regarded as one of the most illustrious and influential legal organizations in California. At its first meeting at the Blue Dolphin Restaurant in San Leandro on June 23, 1970, its organizers envisioned an organization that would serve the trial lawyers in Alameda and Contra Costa Counties through education, networking, business development, and liaisons with the local judges and courts as well as other bar associations.','AG Design Group LAUNCHES a new website for Alameda Contra Costa Trial Lawyers Association www.ACCTLA.org','','publish','open','open','','web-design-walnut-creek-acctla','','','2013-11-11 21:21:40','2013-11-11 21:21:40','',0,'http://agdesigngroup.ag/dev/?p=43',0,'post','',0),
